<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Yogprerna ‚Äî Email Template</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --container-width: 760px;
        --bg: #f6f7f9;
        --card-bg: #ffffff;
        --muted: #6b7280;
        --accent: #1f6feb;
        --highlight: #f4e4a6;
        --heading: #2b2b2b;
        --footer: #9aa0a6;
      }

      html,
      body {
        height: 100%;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto,
          "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--heading);
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 40px 20px;
      }

      .email-wrap {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: var(--container-width);
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 46px 60px;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04),
          0 6px 30px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
      }

      /* --- Logo Section --- */
      .logo {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }
      .logo img {
        height: 64px;
        width: auto;
        display: block;
      }

      /* --- Text and Links --- */
      p {
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin: 14px 0;
        color: #111827;
      }

      .greeting {
        margin-top: 6px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      a {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .hl {
        background: var(--highlight);
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }

      /* --- Footer --- */
      hr.sep {
        border: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
        margin: 28px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--footer);
        text-align: center;
        padding-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .footer .address {
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-top: 6px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .email-wrap {
          padding: 28px 20px;
          margin: 0 8px;
        }
        .logo img {
          height: 48px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <article class="email-wrap" role="article" aria-label="Yogprerna Email">
      <header class="logo">
        <img
          src="<%= process.env.API_BASE_URL %>/logo/logo-black.png"
          alt="Yogprerna"
          style="width: auto; height: 35px"
        />
      </header>

      <section>
        <p class="greeting">Hi <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>

        <p>
          <span class="hl" style="padding: 12">We've</span> updated our
          <a
            href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL %>/<%= legalPolicy.replace(/\\s+/g, `-`).toLowerCase() %>"
            class="hl"
            ><%= legalPolicy %></a
          >
          to support our platform's growth and to better explain our services.
        </p>

        <p>
          You can read the updated terms and policy in full at the links above.
        </p>

        <p>
          These updates take effect immediately. Your continued use of our site
          and services means you accept the updated Terms and acknowledge our
          updated <span class="hl"><%= legalPolicy %></span>.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you have any questions, please feel free to reply to this email or
          write to us at
          <a href="mailto:contact@yogprerna.com">contact@yogprerna.com</a> and
          our team will be happy to assist you.
        </p>

        <p class="signature">
          Thank you for being part of the Yogprerna journey üôè
        </p>

        <p class="signature">Cheers,<br />Team Yogprerna</p>

        <div style="display: flex; gap: 14px">
          <a href="https://x.com/PrernaYog40326">
            <img
              src="<%= process.env.API_BASE_URL %>/social-links/x-twiter.webp"
              alt="Twitter-X"
              style="
                height: 26px;
                width: auto;
                background: white;
                display: inline-block;
                margin-left: 14px;
              "
            />
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/yogprerna">
            <img
              src="<%= process.env.API_BASE_URL %>/social-links/linkedin.webp"
              alt="LinkedIn"
              style="
                height: 26px;
                width: auto;
                background: white;
                display: inline-block;
                margin-left: 14px;
              "
            />
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@yogprerna108">
            <img
              src="<%= process.env.API_BASE_URL %>/social-links/youtube.webp"
              alt="YouTube"
              style="
                height: 26px;
                width: auto;
                background: white;
                display: inline-block;
                margin-left: 14px;
              "
            />
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/yog_prerna/">
